Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:05.98,SignC,,0000,0000,0000,,5 Days Until Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:08.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Christmas great?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.61,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's so exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:12.67,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all have a party on Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:14.95,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:19.50,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas means chicken and cakes, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.37,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Sou, is there anything else you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:24.96,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:28.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas means salmon to me, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:29.63,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Salmon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:32.63,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Why salmon for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:35.01,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with salmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:37.21,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Isn't salmon great?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:10.35,Location,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(382,1)\an7}Watermaple House\N{\fs18}Japan Server \NAkihabara \NCity/ No Monsters \NNo PVP \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:12.82,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Um, isn't this a little too short?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.86,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,My legs are completely visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.94,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.70,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's a perfect fit, Sia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.42,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen centimeters above the knee for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.84,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:27.55,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know a lot about Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:32.00,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,but I believe that Santa Claus \Nwas a man, was he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:33.88,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:36.17,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, Akatsuki's betraying us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:39.46,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,She'll have to be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:46.68,Title,H,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1384,1)}Shattered Wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:44.69,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shattered Wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.98,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're both so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.86,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I could eat a hundred chickens!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.19,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be a snack after dessert!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:01.47,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.94,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,They're wearing miniskirt-Santa and reindeer outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:07.52,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's super-duper cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.39,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Liese, who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:13.04,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reporting to my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:15.55,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.23,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not actually on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:22.67,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,If that monster found out, \Nwho knows what he would say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:23.92,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:25.67,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That was a bit mean of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:28.79,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,My lord is so dedicated to the princess, \NI couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:31.44,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:34.69,HUD1,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(258,1)\an9}Mikakage \N{\fs20}Race/ Human \NDruid, Lv. 78 \NRoderic Merchant Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snack time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.28,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:49.35,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,At first, it was only Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:55.75,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:58.87,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,This fruitcake looks like jewelry, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:03:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:03.76,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're so good at desserts and cooking, Mikakage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:07.02,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,To me, sweets are an art,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:08.76,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,and all other food is just for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.16,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta's food is also good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:16.53,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I get to eat delicious cake \Nwhile I'm protecting the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:17.52,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,This is a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:23.07,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,When are the D.D.D. members coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:27.98,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been told that the attack on \Nthe goblins is going very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:29.83,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,but at earliest, not till after New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.58,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,They won't be back for Christmas, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.58,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But we had a big event planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.18,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's really busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:40.71,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen Shiroe at all lately, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.70,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Is he locked in his room again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:44.11,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:48.99,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Shiroe isn't really the type \Nthat enjoys events like Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.72,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure there's a lot of work \Nto do for the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.79,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.98,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's really tough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.21,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:03.31,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.08,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.73,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:14.46,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,For dressing up like that with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:15.75,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.46,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,They forced me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:22.20,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But you come every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:25.47,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I've been meaning to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.54,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.22,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's my job...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:31.66,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:33.81,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:40.68,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,When did I get so weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.88,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Guarding the princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.92,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I should be happy that my lord is relying on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:50.11,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But when I realize that he's thinking about her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.24,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:57.25,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,If I were like her, would things have \Nbeen different between me and him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:01.90,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But if I were like the princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:06.26,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have been by my \Nlord's side as an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.26,SignA,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H112355&\3c&H5E71AF&}Amenoma
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.60,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.74,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the katana that was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:20.81,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We sold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.70,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.82,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.15,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,They very boldly paid in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.95,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki seems like she's suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:33.45,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Does she seem that way to you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:34.86,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:39.42,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, she isn't the type to let her \Nfeelings show, so it's really obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.46,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:45.09,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki has been coming to observe the D.D.D. training sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:49.34,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I only noticed her there once...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:54.10,SignB,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,5 {\c&H363333&}Days Until Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.19,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like she's been there many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.43,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You know, we work hard to provide
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the best raiding environment in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.80,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But it didn't seem like she wanted to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:04.63,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I reported it to my lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he said to allow her to \Nwatch as much as she liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.86,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he owes Shiroe something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:15.05,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He said to help Akatsuki if anything came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.31,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:21.62,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible she's observing other guilds, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:26.63,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Is she dissatisfied with her level or skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:29.62,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It may be something even more basic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:35.16,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I think what Akatsuki wants is confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:40.26,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose all we can do is to stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:41.94,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:47.27,Location,H,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(380,1)}Duvarcher's Bird Land\N{\fs18}Japan Server\NMihama Area \NField/ Monsters Present \NPVP Permitted \NSkill Use Permitted \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.28,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Teachings...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.95,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe said they're real.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:53.53,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.62,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he says they exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:04.83,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,If my lord says they exist, then they must.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:10.01,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Major combat guilds like D.D.D. \Nand the Black Sword Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.26,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,should have the world's best assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:17.32,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,If they're using the Teachings,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.52,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see those techniques \Nand their power for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Get closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:26.88,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That was pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.11,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Move faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:32.06,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,If I can learn the Teachings, then I, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.16,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.77,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,We're having bouillabaisse today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.41,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be done soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.17,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.17,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.36,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But it turned out really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.85,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And Rudy and the others will be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.64,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.70,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.93,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, she's been really down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.35,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.94,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid, too-perfect middle school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:15.23,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's a brat, a child, and a show-off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.24,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.45,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I see Minori, all I can \Nthink about is how jealous I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.94,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:26.90,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't Minori's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:28.46,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:33.25,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work at least as hard as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:37.63,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best, so I don't cause you problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.51,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:43.27,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Minori helped my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:48.64,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But I was so busy with my own \Nproblems, I couldn't help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.69,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been by his side...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.98,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I can't be useful to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:59.49,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been in a raid, so I'm \Nonly a second-rate assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:02.58,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even buy a first-rate weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:07.09,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my lord didn't take me with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:13.43,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is fight, but I'm weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:18.01,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I were strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.66,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It sure has been lively around here lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.79,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Will they all be back again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:31.52,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we're going into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:33.19,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.96,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,If the adventurers are protecting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.86,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,that must make you feel secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:41.53,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,They say we'll have a delicious \Ncream stew for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.30,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.96,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Adventurer-style?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.30,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:52.18,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, everything's been adventurer-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:55.48,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I even had to wear a costume of \Nsomeone called "Santa Claus" today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:59.73,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I asked them to bring some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.30,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,So that was among them, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.66,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about adventurer clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.83,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,so I wanted them to teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.82,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:15.02,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But wearing clothes you aren't \Nused to is kind of tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:20.03,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know if I should say this, \Nbut you seem to be having a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:25.19,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you've made friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.66,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:31.01,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What? But you look like \Nyou're having so much fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:34.96,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you sometimes feel\Nuncertain or troubled, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.67,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't having fun talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.73,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't like us People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.55,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,They're adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.68,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.56,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,The etiquette I've learned doesn't work with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.23,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If you're having fun, you say you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.96,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If you're sad, you say you're sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.50,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If you're happy, you say you're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:12:00.53,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, they won't know what \Nyou're feeling, so that's what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:05.53,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, I'm lazy, cowardly, and irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:10.30,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about high society or nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:13.17,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,That's just my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:22.42,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she can't be honest with herself \Nbecause she's been expected to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.83,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,be a perfect lady since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:29.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But he's the one exception, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:36.04,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Our march on the goblins is steadily \Nraising the participants' levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.01,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep fighting like this until spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:41.54,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,they'll be a powerful force when \Nthey return to Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.12,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.57,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.36,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:52.83,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want a new toy or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:54.43,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:57.67,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If there's any change, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:03.84,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He's so easy to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:07.85,Location,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(215,1)\an7}Roderic Labs\N{\fs18}Japan Server \NAkihabara \NSeparate Zone/ No Monsters \NPVP Permitted\NEntry Restrictions/ Yes \NExit Restrictions/ Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:06.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do about the ambrosia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:07.85,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.72,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Roderic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.31,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's already night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.95,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it wasn't even noon yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:24.08,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you skip lunch, night will still come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:26.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I have several matters to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,How about joining me for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.58,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's night now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.79,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get some ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.54,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.88,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:46.13,SignA,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H53646D&\3c&H131C3D&\fs26}Ramen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:42.28,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,How's progress with the list I asked you for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:46.13,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You need high-end phantasm- \Nand treasure-class items...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:49.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And quite a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:54.85,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But why include the flavor text?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.87,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,There's some reason, I assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:07.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I understand that we're \Nthe right people to come to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:11.11,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We can work out a way to \Nfinance the research funds,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where other, smaller guilds couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.78,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's none other than Shiroe's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:24.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:26.88,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll need this research eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.85,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Nyanta, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.53,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:41.98,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I just came from the Roderic Merchant Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I know I should've been the one to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.58,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.90,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I got some tasty ramen out of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:55.24,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How's everyone doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:58.03,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The city's excited for Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing's really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:02.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's that time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:06.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What about Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:11.26,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,She's visiting Princess Lenessia daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:13.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:16.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you if there's anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.10,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What did the chief say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:25.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but he said everyone's excited for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:29.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we'll get this \Ndone in time for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.63,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.68,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.89,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:59.36,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You really are strong, Kyouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:01.23,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm level 90, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us the secret to your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.32,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,This is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:11.48,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take it to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:13.42,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It'll brighten the place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.38,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.95,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Sia will be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:20.52,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't call the princess "Sia," should you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:23.44,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,She laughed and looked happy, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.28,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Is that for Naotsugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:32.94,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, when he gets back,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:35.97,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to give him at least \Na little Christmas to enjoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.00,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,A maiden in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.60,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:42.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Henrietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.75,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anyone to give a present to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:45.90,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.87,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:50.07,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.62,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Come on... If you're going to buy it, buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.22,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.30,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.60,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,An unrequited love, from a safe distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:08.67,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling is just a sweet ache I can live with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:13.17,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there are wishes that can't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.55,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten used to that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:25.85,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,Marie's bottomless cheer casts its \Nglow on everyone around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:29.86,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,It may be her self-confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.52,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,But Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.86,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki is so bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:40.87,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't lost the easily injured vulnerability \Nthat grows numb as adulthood sets in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:44.11,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,That vulnerability may be her weak point,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:47.03,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,but it's also a great treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.56,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,Not that she's realized that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:54.88,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,She's so precious, I just want to \Nsqueeze her tight right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:56.93,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:06.55,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Lenessia, you look so cute and fluffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:07.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.77,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I chose it from her wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.03,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:17.04,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Before we get that stew, let's look around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:20.70,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I want Sia to learn more about Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:22.00,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:25.83,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Get too excited, and you'll trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.59,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.59,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,The adventurers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:38.09,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,are so different from us, \NI don't understand them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:44.99,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,Many People of the Land ask me various \Nthings about the adventurers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.60,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:51.13,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,I deal with them every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:53.05,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,but the number of things I don't \Nunderstand keeps rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.11,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, there's one thing I've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:00.89,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,The adventurers are only adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:03.49,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't know the right answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.46,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,it's a mistake to lump them all into a group,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:08.71,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,and merely view them by their jobs or roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.94,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,Even I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.11,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,The adventurers are jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:17.56,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,Each one of them is different,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.68,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,and shines brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:23.42,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,They're special.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.50,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't call myself their friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:33.15,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:42.49,SignA,M,0000,0000,0000,,Restaurant \NMilky Margaret
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:36.09,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The stew here is fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:38.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it's super-duper good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.69,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:42.49,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving you all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.78,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.86,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:52.67,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:59.76,SignA,M,0000,0000,0000,,Restaurant \NMilky Margaret
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:59.76,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Is she going to watch someone train again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:03.00,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki's suffering, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:07.01,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a dagger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.97,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,She's like an obsidian dagger,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.26,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,strong and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:18.78,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I know I can't get stronger simply \Nby watching people train.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:24.32,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the power needed to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:32.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I miss my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:38.67,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to him, just for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.46,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,To get close to him, to tug on his coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:44.11,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,To sit on the same sofa, and look out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:45.81,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,To eat red bean buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:47.70,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be near him always.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.57,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm just in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.97,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But that's just me lying to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:57.56,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't fly anymore, I can't be by my lord's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:03.57,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.64,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:13.38,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I got three salted salmons at Shopping Street 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:16.17,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Sou will be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.36,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.80,SignD,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Enheart Nelreth/ Samurai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:25.80,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.87,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,A PKer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:33.64,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no fighting allowed inside towns!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.51,0:21:37.15,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Guard isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:41.62,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:45.15,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the West Wind Brigade's \Nsecond captain for a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:48.16,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:10.90,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,When his dear friend is wounded, \NSoujirou's rage silently rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.40,0:24:14.05,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Lenessia is forced to make an important decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:16.62,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki runs through the city, lost in thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.99,0:24:20.77,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,As the snow falls, the battle with \Nthe murderer finally begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.03,0:24:24.44,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What secret of the Teachings does \NSoujirou share with Akatsuki?
